data.title: Durning tribes around the world
data.meta_description: Durning genealogy, discover the coat of arms, family crest, family history, ancestry, the surname meaning and the name origin for the Durning Tribe
data.text:
Stay updated on Ireland and your regions of origin with our recommended newspaper, The Business Post. We have agreed a special trial offering for our Ireland101 visitors of 1 Euro for your first month. To sign up, just submit your email here and we will send you the purchase link and the Terms and Conditions, etc. It is a great newspaper and a great way to stay connected every day.

Can you support one of our Heritage Pilot Projects in your region of origin or linked to you surname(s)? We have THREE live pilots on now and we just need pledges from people to help with donations and fundraising.

Project one is a smart upgrade to The Pirate Queen, Grace O’Malley’s home on Clare Island, County Mayo to make it a ‘must visit’ tourist attraction.

Project two is a new ‘must visit’ Heritage Centre attract more Tourists to Carrick-on-Suir in County Tipperary.

Project three is a new Enterprise Centre in Carrick-on-Suir in County Tipperary.

If you would like to help with a donation pledge, or help fundraise, just submit your email here and we will send you more information on the projects and detail on how you can help.
